description: This file is the main entry point for a React-based frontend application. It imports React, ReactDOM, a CSS file, and the App component, then renders the App inside the DOM element with id 'root' within React.StrictMode.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering React components into the DOM.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the DOM node associated with the root.
